1. *Zbilja* je zanimljivo! (It's really interesting!)
2. *Zbilja* sam očekivala da ćeš doći! (I really expected that you would come!)
3. *Zbiljno* nisam mogla da verujem! (I couldn't really believe it!)
4. *Zbiljno* se trudim da uspem! (I'm really trying to make it!)
5. Svi su se *zbiljno* iznenadili! (Everyone was really surprised!)